message.body: Sofie I'm sorry but I just realized I have to attend a volunteer training at MSPCA tomorrow :-[
Ok
I should be free after 3 or 4, I'll text you to see if you've done or not. If not I still want to see how you make those beautiful things with laser cutter
I might not do laser cutter tomorrow I didn't make he files
Happy vday!
Sky u r amazing
I love you
I was so frustrated today at MIT, I just don't know how to talk, I can't find a good timing to talk
And people from MIT are
Not friendly
Really
You r so smart
They r missing out
Just like the feeling i have from Stephanie
I'm always so impressed by what u have to say
I mean the undergrad one. In my group there's a post-doc he is nice, a girl from Wesley is nice too. 2 senior MIT guy just never look at me
I'm so bad to say what I want to say
And I'm not smart, I'm not smart enough to take a MIT class
Yes you r!!! Ur so smart and wise. U just know how to keep your mouth shut when y don't understand.
I just keep talkingp

People in Resnick's class are nice though. I think it's because they are people with passion on education, most people who have passion on education are nice, like Jan, like Azeem, they are supportive
I wish I could talk like you do
Ok, you must be tired, I shouldn't bother you any more, you need rest
No bother me all the time
I mss u sky
I miss you too
I shouldn't have taken that many classes at MIT, I should spend more time here with you guys
It's good to challenge yourself and be brave
You guys inspire me
No it's important to be at MIT. Much better it will change u
I was a coward and I don't know what I want
Why you say that! You're not a coward
Yes I was too nervous to take mit classes
I see you get closer and closer to what you want, I believe you feel that too
I don't know exactly what it is, but you're discovering it
With your unique process
which is very cool and meaningful
I hope your right about discovery
I have no clue about my process being unique or meaningful
It is
You create that unique process
I'm not creating anything, it's just previous training
It's because I'm too slow to figure anything else out
you create your own process and it's definitely unique
If slowly thinking is your model or process, just let it be, follow it
I'm always mean to him
Well u understand
Azeem is silly
I am so mean to him
Tonight
He doesn't care, don't worry, he is very confident about himself, haha
Instead of being mean
I think you're actually helping him
to clarify those ideas he listed
Like Jan said, your questions are the guide
to help him making a more clear mindmap
You see where the problem is, quickly, and you ask question to lead him, just like Jan leads us! This is what I saw today. You're gonna become a super great teacher like Jan, I believe.
Awww
I love jan

Yes he is smart and wise. He can always see the problem and find connection. But he doesn't "teach" us, he just asks questions, we find the answer by ourselves. This is what he told me last semester. And I saw you're doing the same thing to Azeem tonight
Yeah
That makes sense
Sky your really smart and directed I wish I knew myself as well as you know yourself

I don't know myself actually, I am just trying to find out what I want and where I want to be. It takes time, and a lot of experiments, taste as much as you can, in the end you'll find the one you never feel too many, then that's it
I'm jealous that you come here at this young age. I'm still in lost when I was in your age.
You are doing better than I do!
Sky you have such clear goals I feel so lost and and unable to make decisions. I know you will be very successful !
:'( I got mixed up, MSPCA volunteer orientation is next Thursday
You will be very successful Sofie <3 both on career and on relationship, happy valentine's day!!!
